headline: 2 No-Brainer High-Yield Stocks to Buy With $100 Right Now
summary: AGNC Investment has a massive -- and risky -- 16% dividend yield.  Realty Income's yield is 5.6%, backed by 30 annual dividend hikes.  Toronto-Dominion Bank's yield is 4.7%, and it has paid a dividend since 1857.
